&lt;h4 id="prequisitos"&gt;Prequisitos&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ter o &lt;a href="https://brunorozendo.com/post/instalar-adroid-sdk-gnu-linux.html"&gt;android sdk instalado&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id="1-criar-avd"&gt;1. Criar avd&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Uma vez que que já tenha instalado o sdk tudo fica bem mais fácil.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Supondo que queremos rodar uma versão do &lt;code&gt;Android 5.0 (Lollipop)&lt;/code&gt; abra o terminal e vamos instalar os seguites pacotes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;platforms;android-22&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;system-images;android-22;default;x86_64&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;emulator&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;platform-tools&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No terminal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="terminal"&gt;
 &lt;div class="header"&gt;
 &lt;img src="https://brunorozendo.com//images/layouts/shortcodes/terminal.png" alt=""&gt;
 &lt;div class="title"&gt;Terminal&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sdkmanager &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;platforms;android-22&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[=======================================]&lt;/span&gt; 100% Computing updates...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sdkmanager &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;system-images;android-22;default;x86_64&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[=======================================]&lt;/span&gt; 100% Computing updates...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sdkmanager &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;emulator&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[=======================================]&lt;/span&gt; 100% Unzipping... emulator/qemu/linux-
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sdkmanager &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;platform-tools&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[=======================================]&lt;/span&gt; 100% Unzipping... platform-tools/systr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;** Caso queira ver todas as opções possiveis digite no terminal&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>